North America is anticipated to have the highest revenue share during the forecast period, while the Asia Pacific region is predicted to grow at the fastest CAGR during the forecast period. The key players in the immunotoxins market include Amgen Inc., Eisai Co. Ltd., Genentech (Roche), AbbVie Inc., AstraZeneca PLC, Bristol-Myers Squibb Company, Novartis AG, Merck & Co. Inc., Celltech Pharma Ltd., ImmunoGen Inc., BioNTech SE, Macrogenics Inc., Cellerant Therapeutics Inc., Iovance Biotherapeutics Inc., and Zymeworks Inc.
